{"h207b7328g7b7dg48c2gb4a5gf8376dfe22d8": ["Well well. We're popular.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_RD_PostScrying_Astarion.html", "7e0d46c2-4cd5-1de9-2c3e-7dd5e78339cd"], "h63d0fbc6g62bag4bbbga302g2bd8fded9808": ["Seems so. Better watch our backs.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_RD_PostScrying_Astarion.html", "2c96bdc5-34f0-f69f-a987-730b493d23b2"], "h653e7f43g5749g4973ga867ga8b40b744c80": ["Not a problem. I've been watching mine for two hundred years.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_RD_PostScrying_Astarion.html", "fa92d86b-a6b9-a354-545b-05a2cda895de"], "h21e04dd7gfa84g49f6g8de3gbd1ec5199e10": ["I'm not worried. They don't suspect a thing.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_RD_PostScrying_Astarion.html", "3540b083-1db5-75ae-cb1e-f9f3d97c0fe6"], "h4e779ac5g5db9g4528gb871g5da2aabb954c": ["There's nothing wrong with a healthy dose of paranoia, you know.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_RD_PostScrying_Astarion.html", "3d241b56-dcc2-a14a-ee9e-a34238c113d0"], "hbb311521g7b7ag4ebcg8a16g36f31ed5e0b4": ["I'm flattered, but why are they after <i>us</i>?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_RD_PostScrying_Astarion.html", "6aff4c2e-c9df-3dba-8267-7f538f0a41b7"], "h6cebe5c2gd513g4e54gbe11gf0f302054de2": ["Maybe they want to finish what they started? Let's not stop to ask.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_RD_PostScrying_Astarion.html", "c4a133d5-3f4d-6aab-34aa-04c4d20b3ad1"], "he3b7ded9g9ed9g48f0g812eg95ade9d25b26": ["<i>They're </i>hunting me too? Hells' teeth.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_RD_PostScrying_Astarion.html", "fa8c6b09-1f97-a3cb-edb5-8cf979cdafe2"], "h2f45d8beg077dg4c27g935ag8fee50308a5a": ["They're hunting <i>us</i>. We'd better be careful.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_RD_PostScrying_Astarion.html", "91806b5b-206c-d4b6-ad84-95d3de04efbd"], "h763a82a3gf4d6g4782gb360gabaf6fe0d19e": ["Good. Now let's get out of here before they realise just how close we are.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_RD_PostScrying_Astarion.html", "65509dd6-24b5-f2c2-f63e-12b5cc8c9962"], "he600286cga9bag4e0bgb6f5g7b5872d969ab": ["Yes, but why? You're weird, but not <i>that </i>weird.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_RD_PostScrying_Astarion.html", "adea1b6c-ba2e-3725-5e03-8bac7a87c274"]}